northern-gaza/0000018f-8841-d6b6-a59f-facbb18e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军和辛贝特在加沙地带找到了哈马斯扣押的三名以色列人质的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</link><description>沙尼·洛克、阿米特·布斯基拉和伊扎克·格勒伦特都被新星狂欢节劫持为人质。据以色列国防军称，三人从狂欢场跑到梅法西姆交界处，在那里被哈马斯恐怖分子谋杀，尸体被带入加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 16:56:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 224 天：大约 75 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列戈兰高地发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-224-some-75-rockets-fired-at-israels-golan-heights-from-lebanon/0000018f-8759-d7ca-afcf-97fb75770001</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们在加沙找到了 10 月 7 日被哈马斯扣为人质的三名以色列人的尸体。 ■ 以色列向国际法院陈述案情。 ■ 中央司令部：第一批运载援助物资的卡车穿过新建的美国码头进入加沙。 ■ 约 75 枚火箭弹从黎巴嫩发射到以色列戈兰高地高地 ■ 以色列极右活动分子袭击了他们以为正在向加沙运送援助物资的阿拉伯裔以色列卡车司机 ■ 战争进入 224 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 16:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-224-some-75-rockets-fired-at-israels-golan-heights-from-lebanon/0000018f-8759-d7ca-afcf-97fb75770001</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：向以色列北部发射了 75 枚火箭弹；报告：真主党高级指挥官被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-75-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-report-senior-hezbollah-commander-killed/0000018f-8712-d7ca-afcf-97fb78cc0000</link><description>以色列北部社区的两人受轻伤，一所房屋受损</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 15:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-75-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-report-senior-hezbollah-commander-killed/0000018f-8712-d7ca-afcf-97fb78cc0000</guid></item><item><title>出于想法，内塔尼亚胡将拜登和国防部长加兰特视为密谋反对他的阴谋集团</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/out-of-ideas-netanyahu-sees-biden-and-gallant-as-a-cabal-plotting-against-him/0000018f-8663-d443-adef-9febbcf20000</link><description>加沙战争正在变得像1982年开始的黎巴嫩泥潭一样，带有美国在越南失败的味道。但以色列仍然没有战后计划</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 14:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/out-of-ideas-netanyahu-sees-biden-and-gallant-as-a-cabal-plotting-against-him/0000018f-8663-d443-adef-9febbcf20000</guid></item><item><title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，以色列军队似乎正在利用加沙医院、学校作为基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</link><description>卫星图像显示 11 月在土耳其-巴勒斯坦友谊医院周围以及 3 月在 Juhor ad Dik 学校附近修建土堤。上个月，《国土报》发布了卫星图像，显示以色列国防军部队集中在附近的内扎里姆走廊沿线。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 13:43:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/israeli-army-appears-to-be-using-gaza-hospital-school-as-bases-washington-post-reports/0000018f-868c-d443-adef-9fcc60e20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争是悲惨的，但没有发生种族灭绝：以色列在国际法庭上陈述案情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</link><description>以色列提出论点，要求国际法院驳回南非停止在拉法行动并从加沙地带撤军的请求。预计下周将就紧急措施请求做出决定</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 11:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/war-in-gaza-tragic-but-no-genocide-taking-place-israel-presents-its-case-at-world-court/0000018f-85ef-d7f9-a5ff-b5ff9a610000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在对他来说唯一重要的战争中占据上风：保持权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-t