-article/canada-sanctions-four-israelis-over-west-bank-violence/0000018f-82ed-d720-a79f-abff122f0000</guid></item><item><title>即使给以色列带来灾难，内塔尼亚胡和他的伙伴也不会停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-partners-will-not-stop-even-after-bringing-disaster-upon-israel/0000018f-82a5-d430-a38f-c7e51d600000</link><description>战争的延长、总理在国内外的软弱以及以色列正在成为贱民国家的事实只会加剧内塔尼亚胡的救世主情结</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-partners-will-not-stop-even-after-bringing-disaster-upon-israel/0000018f-82a5-d430-a38f-c7e51d600000</guid></item></channel></rss>